title: 241: If We Could Relive A Moment From Our Lives | Ear Biscuits Ep.241
description:
Looking back at two very different point in their lives, R&L discuss what specific point they would relive if there were no consequences that followed. Listen to R&L share those moments as well as their slightly controversial opinion on music through the generations on this episode of Ear Biscuits!
